text: This obsoletes IRM 4.60.5, International Procedures, Classiﬁcation of International-feature
The material in this IRM section is obsolete because subject matter experts in international practice areas no longer classify returns with international features.
IRM 4.60.5, International Procedures, Classiﬁcation of International feature-Returns, dated September 1, 2004 is obsolete as of the date of this transmittal.
LB&I, SB/SE, TE/GE management and examiners
